2. High-Level BuzzFlow E2E Workflow

End-to-end flow:

1. Lead captured from landing page / product / form / ad.


2. Your backend (or Stripe checkout success) hits the BuzzFlow CRM Engine API.


3. Engine creates/updates a Lead in Pipedrive.


4. Pipedrive sends webhook events back to the engine.


5. Engine writes those events into Firestore under buzzflow_crm/....


6. React dashboard reads from Firestore → shows real-time leads & deals.


7. (Optional) Your AI/automation layer (BuzzGPT, etc.) reads Firestore + suggests actions / sends messages.


8. You get repeatable, visible, auditable sales flow with zero spreadsheet chaos.



This stack can live as its own project, nothing else required.


